  <description>Adds Mass Effect biotic powers as Vanilla Psycasts Expanded paths (Adept, Vanguard, Sentinel). Biotics require the Eezo Nodules gene and a Biotic Amp implant. Asari are naturally biotic when the ME(b) - Asari mod is installed.</description>

